 .SH TROUBLESHOOTING

 .SS Bot won't start
 .RS
 1. Verify DISCORD_TOKEN is valid in .env
 2. Check Python version: \fBpython3 --version\fR
 3. View logs: \fBtail -f ron.log\fR
 4. Ensure network connection is active
 .RE

 .SS Commands not appearing in Discord
 .RS
 1. Run \fB!sync\fR to manually sync commands
 2. Verify bot has "applications.commands" scope
 3. Check bot has appropriate permissions in server
 .RE

